Class LStack<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • Crazy8.LStack<T>

  • public class LStack<T>
extends Object
    LSTack useses the LinkedList methods and structure to recreate a stack class for Java. This remasks, effectively, some of the methods as more accessible one, and conforms to the general idea of what a stack is.
